{"tid":1883031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★武漢肺炎】紅磡觀音廟借庫取消","createTime":"2020-02-16T15:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T06:27:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f076baadb2a99825d43d17599cf049df96ff7a67","tid":1883031,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200214/photo/bkn-20200214001756540-0214_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200214003829\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200214001756540-0214_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200214003829&h=b0331421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情愈趨嚴重，今年的觀音借庫活動也要取消。農曆正月廿六、即本月十九日是每年一度觀音開庫大日子，當中以紅磡觀音廟最為熱鬧，晚上十一時起通宵開放供善信借庫，借庫金額由三千萬至十億元不等。其次是大坑蓮花宮及筲箕灣天后廟，也香火鼎盛。<br />\n不過，華人廟宇委員會在紅磡觀音廟貼出通告，表示考慮到過往到紅磡觀音廟借庫的善信人數眾多，為減低現時新型冠狀病毒感染的風險，觀音廟在今年二月十八至十九日的觀音開庫將會取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200214/bkn-20200214001756540-0214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200214%2Fbkn-20200214001756540-0214_00822_001.html&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=5f238452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200214/bkn-20200214001756540-0214_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"505b00ed18743227dff0d93b45e5e69c91a08816","tid":1883031,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"no $$$借<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809ab59904e5feaac75a29b027c460c3d5f99043","tid":1883031,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=